*config-kernel-0.3.3 (03 Apr 2004)

  03 Apr 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.3.0.ebuild,
  config-kernel-0.3.1.ebuild, config-kernel-0.3.3.ebuild:
  Bump for a few fixes that are only problems if one messes with 05kernel by
  hand. Remove a few older versions.

*config-kernel-0.3.2-r1 (03 Apr 2004)

  03 Apr 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org>
  config-kernel-0.3.2-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump. We should not enable koutput by default.

*config-kernel-0.3.2 (02 Apr 2004)

  02 Apr 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.2.8.ebuild,
  config-kernel-0.2.9.ebuild, config-kernel-0.3.2.ebuild:
  Bump to fix --output-dir default, and remove a few older builds.

*config-kernel-0.3.1 (26 Mar 2004)

  26 Mar 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.3.1.ebuild:
  Okay, symlink stuff really fixed now. Silly edge cases.

*config-kernel-0.3.0 (26 Mar 2004)

  26 Mar 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.2.7.ebuild,
  config-kernel-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Bump to finally fix --set-symlink when /usr/src/linux isn't there at all.
  Removed one stale old version.

*config-kernel-0.2.9 (26 Mar 2004)

  26 Mar 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.2.9.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Bump. small fix for setting the symlink if /usr/src/linux didn't exist before
  (thanks johnm). Commiting now x86. Changed herd to "kernel"

*config-kernel-0.2.8 (25 Mar 2004)

  25 Mar 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.2.8.ebuild:
  Bump. Includes fixes to --make-koutput. Added -v/--version flag.

*config-kernel-0.2.7 (25 Mar 2004)

  25 Mar 2004; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> config-kernel-0.2.7.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Initial commit of config-kernel. This is in preparation for the great koutput
  changeover.

